summary: Organized, task oriented professional with experience in customer support. Background includes skilled active listener, strong customer service experience and ability to respond to the end-user in a business professional manner. I am highly effective in using technical domain knowledge. Self-starter committed to taking ownership and capable of completing assigned projects independently and in a team environment.

experience.title: Telephone Interviewer
experience.description: Performs telephone interviews for surveys and censuses; telephones respondents to gain cooperation; obtains and records data on survey instruments; reviews information for completeness and assists in clerical processing of collected information; migrated thousands of documents into ECM and sunset legacy Intranet Server into a SharePoint environment; contributed to document categorization, metadata application and publishing for internal viewing; explained SharePoint concepts and facilitated collaboration and information sharing.

experience.title: Customer Service Representative
experience.description: Handled customer questions, complaints, and billing inquiries; resolved issues with one-call resolution; proactively offered alternative solutions to retain business; managed activations of new customer accounts; communicated with customers; frequently made financial decisions to protect/collect revenues and adjust customer accounts.

experience.title: Sales Executive
experience.description: Secured potential client information to establish new internet service; monitored and reported on sales activities; advised customers on forthcoming product developments and promotions; reviewed personal sales performance, aimed to meet or exceed targets, and ensured customer satisfaction and quality of product and service delivery.

experience.title: Stocking Associate
experience.description: Received materials into the store and prepared for shelves; checked deliveries for accuracy; organized stock room for labeling and placement; contributed to reducing store shrinkage by researching inventory discrepancies; communicated with partners about new arrivals, overages/shortages, and delivery delays; supported loss prevention efforts.
